name: Rise Out From Dungeons
overview: Rise Out From Dungeons is a platform game where you must guide an unnamed character through 20 dungeons avoiding traps and blue-colored men. The graphics and game mechanics are strikingly similar to Lode Runner, but with a twist. The objective in each dungeon is simply to "rise out" from them, and that can be done by climbing a stair which passes through the dungeon ceiling.
